title: Day 1310
content:
# Day 1310

Man what a roller coaster of emotions it is when your child's birth is near and I say this as the man. I just act as support for the woman who has to do all the heavy lifting. Can only imagine what Paige is feeling right now.

Dear Lord please give my wife a safe, happy, healthy birth tomorrow. I can't thank you enough for all the blessings you have given us. In your name, Jesus Christ, the King of kings, we pray.

Beyond excited to meet my little boy, Ryder, tomorrow. The future is bright :)

10/22/25

Conor Jay Chepenik
